<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
    <head>
        <title>Minecraft Server Uptime Monitor</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/style.css">
    </head>
    <body>
        <main class="mdc-layout">
            <h1 class="mdc-typography--headline4 mdc-title">
                FTS427 ZHServer 服务器在线率监控器
            </h1>

            <section class="mdc-section">
                <div class="mdc-chip-set">
                    <span class="mdc-chip mdc-chip--success">绿色方块: 在线</span>
                    <span class="mdc-chip mdc-chip--warning">黄色方块: 高延迟</span>
                    <span class="mdc-chip mdc-chip--error">红色方块: 离线</span>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="mdc-section">
                <div class="mdc-typography--subtitle1">
                    <span style="color: #eeeeee;">当前服务器状态: </span>
                    <span style="color: {{color1}};">{{status}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="mdc-typography--subtitle1">
                    <span style="color: #eeeeee;">过去 3 天内在线率: </span>
                    <span style="color: {{color2}};">{{rate}}</span>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="mdc-section">
                <div class="mdc-typography--body2" style="color: #eeeeee;">
                    详细在线信息(采样间隔 30s, 取最近 8640 次采样数据, 时间从前往后):
                </div>
                <div class="blocks-container">
                    {{{verbose}}}
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
    </body>
</html>
